This is a Tampermonkey/Violentmonkey userscript targeting MacOS users on Chrome, that are fed up with Outlook Web hijacking their Alt/Option key when editing text.
This might work on Firefox, but it's not tested.

Source code should be easy enough to understand with the comments provided.

You will need to use https://www.tampermonkey.net/scripts.php or https://violentmonkey.github.io/ (untested).

Contributions are welcome, but feel free to fork.
